Steps to build project:
Setup Project: Create a Vite React TypeScript project and install Tailwind CSS.

Folder Structure : Organize contexts/, components/, types/, AppProviders.tsx, and App.tsx.

Define Types :Create Todo, FilterType, and ThemeType in types/index.ts.

TodoContext : Use useReducer for CRUD + clear completed; persist todos in localStorage.

FilterContext : Use useState to track current filter (all, active, completed).

ThemeContext : Use useState to track theme; apply .dark class to <html>; persist in localStorage.

AppProviders : Wrap App with ThemeProvider > TodoProvider > FilterProvider.

Components : Build TodoInput, TodoList, TodoItem, FilterButtons, ThemeToggleButton using Tailwind.

Filtering & Dark Mode :Filter todos based on context; toggle dark mode globally with Tailwind classes.
: Ensure CRUD, filtering, dark/light theme, and localStorage persistence all work.


